author: Patrick Reevell
title: Putin dons hazmat suit, as Russia admits virus numbers likely far higher
description: Russia's President Vladimir Putin donned a hazmat suit to visit a hospital housing coronavirus patients in Moscow, as Russia admitted its numbers were likely much higher.
content:
Russias President Vladimir Putin donned a hazmat suit and breathing mask during a visit to a hospital housing coronavirus patients in Moscow on Tuesday, as the Russian government signalled the virus outbreak is becoming increasingly serious in the country.
